<br>
A moment's consideration tells her the beams are strong enough to hold her weight, and she quickly makes her way up onto the superstructure.  &quot;It's been a while, but I believe I still remember how to do this,&quot; she jokes lightly.  &quot;My one domestic skill.&quot;   <br>
<br>
Indeed, it was almost true.  The young Lysia had spent as little time indoors as possible, too restless to learn more than the most basic rudiments of sewing or cooking.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hippolyte>Hippolyte</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 760<br> <font color=#993300>(2/16/03 9:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=33>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.themiscrya.i-p.com/Hippwknife1ezboard.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Preparing.</span><hr size=1> Hippolyte walked over to the pile of fronds and then offered them up to Lysia.  &quot;Here are more that we can tie onto the structure.  If you will take these and start.. I will go get a few more so that we can finish.&quot; <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>

