<br>
In a soft almost whisper, Hippolyte began to chant prayers to Hera.  Calling for a safe mission for the women.  There were not many of them...but there were enough.  Just enough Hippolyte believed to make a dent in the pride of the Roman men. <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>

